data.description: Investors? Looking to add to your portfolio with extra cash flow? Beautiful corner home with a 2 1/2 car garage on a easily maintainable lot in the great area of Dolton! Well kept home with many great professional updates. Windows upstairs installed by Feldco in 2019. Hot water tank only 1 year old. Central air and duct work newly installed in 2021. New fire resistant doors installed throughout the interior of the home in 2021. Front and back storm/security doors newly installed by Feldco in 2021. New toilets in both full bathrooms and updated vanity and sink in the bathroom upstairs in 2021. Overflow valve was professionally installed in the basement to prevent water back up from the sewer outside on the corner. Great $7,000 investment and no issues since installed in early 2022. New gas line installed for the kitchen stove in 2019. New garage door system installed in 2022. Concrete patio installed in 2021. High rent for good passive income. Schedule your showings before the highest and best is called for!
